        <mxCell id="jQ3XhOnWibMsG6wDfxci-24" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Question: How do the SP access your ADLS?&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;The applciation authenticates using the client credentials to Entry ID, receives OAuth Token and then authorization is enforced using RBAC and ACL permissions on ADLS.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
